{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/passion/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"halfbs"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"8ecf437f-8746-5c58-80fe-1771bc2682aa","excerpt":"Passion is not mastery, Our convictions take courage,  Our souls cry for others, We are finite, Things are euphoric or vicious, It is beautiful to be bold and unabashed, Passion is not expertise, Between the empathetic and apathetic,","html":"<p>Passion is not mastery,</p>\n<hr>\nStrong feelings are\n<hr>\nneither facts nor keen understanding.\n<hr>\n<p>Our convictions take courage,</p>\n<hr>\nto swim against the current,\n<hr>\nto be true.\n<hr>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1024px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/halfbs/static/afd33f0c367603d3a4bff58c8202cbe1/2bef9/diving-bell.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"diving-bell\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/halfbs/static/afd33f0c367603d3a4bff58c8202cbe1/2bef9/diving-bell.png\"\n        srcset=\"/halfbs/static/afd33f0c367603d3a4bff58c8202cbe1/72799/diving-bell.png 320w,\n/halfbs/static/afd33f0c367603d3a4bff58c8202cbe1/6af66/diving-bell.png 640w,\n/halfbs/static/afd33f0c367603d3a4bff58c8202cbe1/2bef9/diving-bell.png 1024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\nThat ceaseless flow spares no one.\n<hr>\nWe drown in knowledge,\n<hr>\nand we feel we know that ocean.\n<hr>\n<p>Our souls cry for others,</p>\n<hr>\nour minds eject what they can\n<hr>\nto take on new horrors, bold.\n<hr>\n<p>We are finite,</p>\n<hr>\nfoaming at the mouth,\n<hr>\nof infinite arrays of information, in scores.\n<hr>\nWe know enough to react,\n<hr>\nbut often not enough,\n<hr>\nto prevent the tragedies that come our way, and more.\n<hr>\n<p>Things are euphoric or vicious,</p>\n<hr>\nand then,\n<hr>\nthey are washed away.\n<hr>\nFor many, a lack of knowledge leads to\n<hr>\nfanaticism on the subject at hand.\n<hr>\nThey attack what they don’t grasp,\n<hr>\nand sway.\n<hr>\n<p>It is beautiful to be bold and unabashed,</p>\n<hr>\nbut propaganda works best on the beautiful, alas.\n<hr>\nLook carefully before you misguide another’s gaze,\n<hr>\nbefore lunging into false battles,\n<hr>\nwith no end in sight, and pass.\n<hr>\n<p>Passion is not expertise,</p>\n<hr>\nbut neither is a restrained armchair view.\n<hr>\nAnd I’d take the passionate over the poised any day,\n<hr>\nwith delight, anew.\n<hr>\n<p>Between the empathetic and apathetic,</p>\n<hr>\nthe former will get informed,\n<hr>\nAs long as they’re not caught up\n<hr>\nin some performance,\n<hr>\nthey’ll learn, and be transformed.\n<hr>","frontmatter":{"title":"Passion is not mastery","date":"December 29, 2023"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/passion/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/basorexia-agkorexia/"},"frontmatter":{"tags":["kitty","lust","despair","longing","long-distance","bliss"],"title":"Basorexia, agkorexia"}},"next":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["712016698"],"slicesMap":{}}